snippet.title: TikToker Beats Her Daughter To Death & Makes TikTok Dance Videos Weeks Later
snippet.description:
Rest In Peace Kaylee-Jayde Priest 

Small TikToker Nicola Preist would post TikTok videos with her daughter Kaylee-Jayde throughout the lockdown.

When the videos ended however Nicola would beat her daughter. On the 8th of August 2020 its believed that either Nicola or her boyfriend Callum Redfern subjected Kaylee-Jayde to a beating which resulted in her death.
